    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`ProposalQueued(uint id, uint eta)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Emitted when a proposal has been queued in the Timelock.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
