    }}>{`ProposalExecuted`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`ProposalExecuted(uint id)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Emitted when a proposal has been executed in the Timelock.`}</p>
