      "id": "read-only-functions-uni"
    }}>{`Read-Only Functions: UNI`}</h1>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "get-current-votes"
    }}>{`Get Current Votes`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function getCurrentVotes(address account) returns (uint96)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the balance of votes for an account as of the current block.`}</p>
