        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <h1 {...{
      "id": "read-only-functions-governor-alpha"
    }}>{`Read-Only Functions: Governor Alpha`}</h1>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "quorum-votes"
    }}>{`Quorum Votes`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function quorumVotes() public pure returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the minimum number of votes required for a proposal to succeed.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "proposal-threshold"
    }}>{`Proposal Threshold`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function proposalThreshold() returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the minimum number of votes required for an account to create a proposal.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "proposal-max-operations"
    }}>{`Proposal Max Operations`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function proposalMaxOperations() returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the maximum number of actions that can be included in a proposal. Actions are functions calls that will be made when a proposal succeeds and executes.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "voting-delay"
    }}>{`Voting Delay`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function votingDelay() returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the number of blocks to wait before voting on a proposal may begin. This value is added to the current block number when a proposal is created.`}</p>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "voting-period"
    }}>{`Voting Period`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function votingPeriod() returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Returns the duration of voting on a proposal, in blocks.`}</p>
