    <h1 {...{
      "id": "state-changing-functions-governor-alpha"
    }}>{`State-Changing Functions: Governor Alpha`}</h1>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "propose"
    }}>{`Propose`}</h2>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-solidity"
      }}>{`function propose(address[] memory targets, uint[] memory values, string[] memory signatures, bytes[] memory calldatas, string memory description) returns (uint)
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Creates a Proposal to change the protocol.`}</p>
